<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>والبخاري في <span class="c1">"الكبير"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ١/ ١٠٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
