<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>والطبراني في <span class="c1">"الأوسط"</span> <span class="c2">(٨٩٢٧)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
